short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export URLs, titles, and domains of all open tabs to a CSV file.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension examines all open tabs across all open chrome windows and exports the url and the page title as a two column CSV file for further inspection and editing in a spreadsheet or other application. The aim is to help researchers and developers manage swathes of open tabs created when exploring a new topic.
